==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Gratitude
<hw>Grat"i*tude</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>gratitude</ets>, LL. <ets>gratitudo</ets>, from <ets>gratus</ets>
agreeable, grateful. See <er>Grate</er>, <pos>a.</pos>]</ety> <def>The
state of being grateful; warm and friendly feeling toward a benefactor;
kindness awakened by a favor received; thankfulness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The debt immense of endless <qex>gratitude.</qex></q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gratuitous</ent>⟦br⟧
